:: WDS-120 The smell [nobr avatar-wds-night nighttime]
<<silently>>
<<set $header.location to "MOTEL COURT">>
<<set $header.time to "Wednesday night">>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>
/* %%% HUMAN-DRAFT %%%
   WDS-120 The smell — First dose: wet dog, rut, oily animal smell; her body answers and judgment starts to dull.
   Intent: structural placeholder only; includes low Composure check. ~90 words.
   %%% END %%% */

<<set _checkSkill to (typeof $player.currentComposure === "number") ? $player.currentComposure : $player.skills.composure.level>>
<<skillCheck "Composure" "2d6" _checkSkill 7>>
<<success>>
/* %%% HUMAN-DRAFT %%%
   WDS-120 success — She stays clear enough to keep reading.
   Intent: structural placeholder only; texture branch, outcome unchanged.
   %%% END %%% */

[[You look for the source.|WDS-125 At the edge of the light]]
<<failure>>
