:: WDS-160 Driving it off [nobr avatar-wds-night nighttime]
<<silently>>
<<set $header.location to "MOTEL COURT">>
<<set $header.time to "Wednesday night">>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>
/* %%% HUMAN-DRAFT %%%
   WDS-160 Driving it off — Close range with the creature/source while half-dosed; she sprays it.
   Intent: structural placeholder only; includes high spine Composure/Confrontation check. It recoils regardless. ~100 words.
   %%% END %%% */

<<set _composureSkill to (typeof $player.currentComposure === "number") ? $player.currentComposure : $player.skills.composure.level>>
<<set _checkSkill to Math.max(_composureSkill, $player.skills.confrontation.level)>>
<<skillCheck "Composure / Confrontation" "2d6" _checkSkill 9>>
<<success>>
<<set $player.flags.wdsSpineHeld to true>>
/* %%% HUMAN-DRAFT %%%
   WDS-160 success — She holds through musk and fear and gets the spray off cleanly.
   Intent: structural placeholder only; possible Composure skill grant later.
   %%% END %%% */

[[It breaks away from the light.|WDS-165 Into the dark]]
<<failure>>
<<set $player.flags.wdsSpineFailed to true>>
/* %%% HUMAN-DRAFT %%%
   WDS-160 failure — She nearly goes under at arm's length, but gets the can up and fires anyway; it recoils.
   Intent: structural placeholder only; grants +1 incident influence later, outcome unchanged.
   %%% END %%% */

[[It breaks away from the light anyway.|WDS-165 Into the dark]]
<</skillCheck>>
<</page>>


:: WDS-165 Into the dark [nobr avatar-wds-night nighttime]
<<silently>>
<<if not $player.flags.wdsInfluenceGranted>>
    <<set _wdsInfluence to 2>>
    <<if $player.flags.wdsDeepFailed or $player.flags.wdsSpineFailed>>
        <<set _wdsInfluence to 3>>
    <</if>>
    <<set $nyse.influence += _wdsInfluence>>
    <<set $player.flags.wdsInfluenceGranted to true>>
<</if>>
<<if not $player.flags.wdsSkillGranted>>
    <<if $player.flags.wdsVectorReasoned>>
        <<set $player.skills.academic.level += 1>>
    <<elseif $player.flags.wdsSpineHeld>>
        <<set $player.skills.composure.level += 1>>
    <<else>>
        <<set $player.skills.streetwise.level += 1>>
    <</if>>
    <<set $player.flags.wdsSkillGranted to true>>
<</if>>
<<set $header.location to "MOTEL COURT">>
<<set $header.time to "Wednesday night">>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>
/* %%% HUMAN-DRAFT %%%
   WDS-165 Into the dark — The creature/source recoils, breaks, and runs beyond the highway light into the trees; the lot goes quiet except for vending buzz.
   Intent: structural placeholder only; guarded NYSE influence and skill grant fire here. ~90 words.
   %%% END %%% */

[[The guests begin coming back.|WDS-170 Coming back]]
<</page>>


